## Additional Terms for Agricultural Use

This software is specifically designed to support agricultural communities and 
farming operations. While the MIT license allows commercial use, we encourage 
users to:

1. Support local farming communities
2. Contribute improvements back to the open source project
3. Use the platform responsibly and ethically
4. Respect data privacy and user rights

